#

Kefir and Fruit Parfait

10 min
$5.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Fat

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastSnackHealthy

Description

A refreshing and nutritious parfait layered with creamy kefir and fresh fruits, perfect for a quick breakfast or snack.

Ingredients

  • kefir: 1 cup
  • mixed berries (strawberries, blueberries, raspberries): 1 cup
  • granola: 1/2 cup
  • honey (optional): 1 tbsp
  • chopped nuts (almonds, walnuts): 2 tbsp
